{"type": "article", "id": 25306, "title": "像积木拼接的大理石茶几", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-12T06:35:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121053xV1geNZScXu62HYn.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组茶几使用了白色的卡拉拉大理石（Carrara marble），用三块经过切割好的板像积木一样拼接。两块十字交叉构成桌腿，上面再扣上一块作为桌面，结构巧妙且方便拆装和运输。一定程度上解决大理石做较大型家具时不易运输的缺陷。此外，茶几简单的形状和白色纹路让茶几显得轻盈而灵活。<a href=\"http://www.alfredo-haeberli.com/work/tables/12-215/riviera_marble_edition\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121051JoBfFGPyCQ0WUXR2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121052Xue17sB0kWJL3HVy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121053OYX9RoscI6ejtdnK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121053WuyPXok2MBDU3xhi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}